invalid type: string "Logistics Q&A Document  \n1. What is Logistics?  \nLogistics is the process of planning, implementing, and controlling the movement and storage of goods \nfrom origin to consumption.  \n2. What is Supply Chain Management?  \nIt is the coordination of production, shipment, and delivery of goods.  \n3. What is Inventory Management?  \ntion-after[validate_required_fields(), Task